ZH: 我的妈妈是一名教师。
EN: My mother is a teacher.

ZH: 我想要成为一名优秀的教师。
EN: I want to become an excellent teacher.

ZH: 那位年轻的教师对学生很有耐心。
EN: That young teacher is very patient with students.

ZH: 我们学校的教师团队非常团结。
EN: The teaching team at our school is very united.

ZH: 这位教师教授英语和历史。
EN: This teacher teaches English and History.

ZH: 教师们每天都在努力教学生。
EN: Teachers work hard to teach students every day.

ZH: 这个学校有一百名教师。
EN: This school has one hundred teachers.

ZH: 她是我们学校最好的教师之一。
EN: She is one of the best teachers in our school.

ZH: 教师应该给学生树立榜样。
EN: Teachers should set a good example for students.

ZH: 教师们都参加了教育培训。
EN: Teachers have all participated in educational training.

ZH: 那位教师总是对学生很严格。
EN: That teacher is always very strict with students.

ZH: 我的朋友正在上教师培训课程。
EN: My friend is taking a teacher training course.

ZH: 这位教师很会激励学生。
EN: This teacher is good at motivating students.

ZH: 教师们每周都要准备很多教案。
EN: Teachers have to prepare a lot of lesson plans every week.

ZH: 这所学校正在招募新的教师。
EN: This school is recruiting new teachers.

ZH: 教师节是一个庆祝教师的节日。
EN: Teacher's Day is a holiday to celebrate teachers.

ZH: 这位教师经验丰富，教学效果很好。
EN: This teacher is experienced and has a good teaching effect.

ZH: 学校为教师举行了一场感恩晚会。
EN: The school held a Thanksgiving party for the teachers.

ZH: 这位教师总是鼓励学生尝试新事物。
EN: This teacher always encourages students to try new things.

ZH: 教师们对学生成绩很在意。
EN: Teachers care a lot about students' grades.
